Rules

1) Two players only
2) One dice only
3) First player to reach 100 points (score) wins
  - Cumulative points (rolls add up)
4) Rolling a "1" resets all points you've accumulated in your turn
5) Choosing to pass the turn to the other player allows you to save the points you have so far

